    "body": "For security reasons, we right now do not support `eth_sendTransaction` or `eth_sign`. As @tynes stated, the way to interact with the node is to create an `ethers.Wallet` as follows:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst wallet = new ethers.Wallet(privatekey, l2Provider)\r\nawait wallet.signMessage(...)\r\n...\r\n```",
